title: Nano
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-owned and operated with no printed menus. There is always at least one vegetarian (sometimes vegan) soup, and usually one vegetarian main dish. Also serves salads. Seasonal menu. Available for bookings in the evenings for groups of 8 or more. If opened for an evening booking and someone walks by, they will be made welcome if there is a table available.
